Class WinterRestaurantMenuFactory

java.lang.Object
RestaurantMenuBuilderAbstractFactoryStarterCode.app.src.main.java.menu_factory.WinterRestaurantMenuFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
RestaurantMenuFactory
public class WinterRestaurantMenuFactory extends Object implements RestaurantMenuFactory
WinterRestaurantMenuFactory is responsible for creating components of the winter menu, including drinks, entrees, main courses, and desserts. This factory follows the abstract factory design pattern to produce seasonal menu items.
Author:
Gurnoor Kaur
